Module it.polimi.ingsw
Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.view.gui

Class Gui

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
it.polimi.ingsw.client.view.gui.Gui
All Implemented Interfaces:
UserInterface, PropertyChangeListener, EventListener
public class Gui extends javafx.application.Application implements UserInterface, PropertyChangeListener
This class is the Gui of the game. It has attributes and methods that allow the player to correctly play the game and to correctly display various messages and data based on the local state of the game.
Author:
Marco Galli, Luca Guffanti
